To uninstal the nvida driers:

systemctl stop ligthdm
sudo pacman -R nvidia-440xx-utils
sudo pacman -R linux57-nvidia-440xx lnux58-nvidia-440xx linux414-nvidia-440xx lb32-nvidia-440xx-utils nvidia-prime
sudo pacman -S linux57-nvidia-450xx linux58-nvidia-450xx lb32-nvidia-450xx-utils nvidia-prime linux414-nvidia-450xx nvidia-450xx-utils
systemctl start ligthdm

Then on manajaro settins manager uninstall the old driver and install the correct driver version
